17.5.1 RIGHT OF FIRST REFUSAL FOR LOCATION. In the event of termination or expiration of this Agreement, should the parties choose not to negotiate a successor Franchise Agreement under which the Franchisee would continue to operate the Franchised Restaurant at the Location, BKC or its designated representative shall be granted the opportunity, subject to acquiring any required governmental approval:

1. To acquire the property or leasehold interest at the Location;
2. To purchase the assets related to the Franchised Restaurant located at the Location;
3. Or both (1) and (2) above. This right shall supersede any third-party offer made within a reasonable timeframe, but shall not obligate BKC or its representative to exercise this option.
